Package com.olegtoropoff.petcareappointment.utils

Class UrlMapping

java.lang.Object
com.olegtoropoff.petcareappointment.utils.UrlMapping
public class UrlMapping extends Object
Defines URL mappings for the application's API endpoints.

This class organizes endpoint paths for various resources, such as users, appointments, pets, photos, reviews, veterinarians, patients, authentication, roles, and biographies. The mappings are structured for clarity and easy maintenance.
